{"tid":2176131,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"岩岩發夢見到過左生既老豆問我睇唔睇鋪","createTime":"2020-08-27T02:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T17:45:24.000Z","uid":44559,"like":185,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"5f5f8897e2c077e7e91e2ffcadfd76817cca8c7a","tid":2176131,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T02:00:52.000Z","msg":"岩岩發夢見到過左生既老豆<br />\n佢話岩岩有人請左佢睇鋪 睇下層<br />\n而家搵緊人睇第間 第2層 問我睇唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最尾我問佢幾點出門口 佢話要6點到XX<br />\n我見重有1個鐘諗主拎杯水比佢 跟住就醒左<br />\n<br />\n起身我開始諗點解要睇鋪做野 明明燒左好多野比佢<br />\n再諗諗下 我係咪就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7137891879032c9694171b81961becda6e935df9","tid":2176131,"uid":8175,"like":170,"dislike":3,"score":167,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T02:02:07.000Z","msg":"即係叫你落去陪佢呀<br />\n樓主 rip"},{"pid":"a09b443632242289add6fe6d39e52c4a35c1b936","tid":2176131,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7137891879032c9694171b81961becda6e935df9","tid":2176131,"uid":8175,"like":170,"dislike":3,"score":167,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T02:02:07.000Z","msg":"即係叫你落去陪佢呀<br />\n樓主 rip"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T02:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25df3fd1905aab5645092580d3dc26eab2cebcef","tid":2176131,"uid":44559,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"molamola"},{"pid":"b88d916bbdc6e5dbfe8a6fb14a814977679b7d10","tid":2176131,"uid":2757,"like":151,"dislike":1,"score":150,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T02:11:02.000Z","msg":"燒隻公仔幫手睇舖，同佢講你好忙，唔得閒睇舖...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a8003f308e85a8462c8ebcf47d7030e5505f9f","tid":2176131,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f5f8897e2c077e7e91e2ffcadfd76817cca8c7a","tid":2176131,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T02:0